data.description: This beautiful home boasts (on the main floor) original hardwood floors, beautiful wood trim, a fireplace with original tile, a large dining room, and a main floor laundry/mud room space. The kitchen has been recently updated with a large 6x8 walk in pantry space, a gas cooktop, electric double ovens, and gorgeous stone countertops with the sink overlooking the large double lot! On the second floor you will find an open landing/flex space 3 large bedrooms all with substantial walk in closets for the age of the home, and the second full bathroom (currently being renovated). There's ample storage space in the basement along with a partially finished space that could be used as a 4th bedroom and an additional family room! Professional photos coming soon!
